Short:        DevilutionX (Diablo engine)
Author:       Joni Valtanen
Uploader:     Joni Valtanen
Type:         game/actio
Version:      1.0.1-git20200330
Requires:     PowerSDL >= 16.1
Architecture: ppc-morphos >= 3.13
URL:          https://github.com/diasurgical/devilutionX

Diablo build for modern operating systems.

Installation:
-------------

- Extract the files in the lha
- Copy diabdat.mpq from your CD (or GoG install folder) to the DevilutionX-MOS folder
- Run devilutionx

Features:
---------

- The configurations and save games are located program folder
- Multiplayer is not supported

